query:
UPDATE charging_processes
        SET
            start_date = $1,
            end_date = $2,
            charge_energy_added = $3,
            start_ideal_range_km = $4,
            end_ideal_range_km = $5,
            start_battery_level = $6,
            end_battery_level = $7,
            duration_min = $8,
            outside_temp_avg = $9,
            position_id = $10,
            address_id = $11,
            start_rated_range_km = $12,
            end_rated_range_km = $13,
            geofence_id = $14,
            charge_energy_used = $15,
            cost = $16,
            charging_status = $17
        WHERE id = $18
